56.3	Simon_Fuller	Simon Fuller	Simon Fuller (born 17 May 1960) is a British artist manager, television producer and creator of the Idol franchise, first seen as Pop Idol in the UK. Fuller is also the co-creator and executive producer of the Fox TV reality show So You Think You Can Dance and other U.S. and European TV shows.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0e/Simon_Fuller_-_357_-_Head_Shot_-_8X10.jpg/200px-Simon_Fuller_-_357_-_Head_Shot_-_8X10.jpg
